ChickpeaAscoDispersal: Research Compendium for the Paper 'The role of conidia in the dispersal of Ascochyta rabiei'

Source: R/ChickpeaAscoDispersal-package.R
ChickpeaAscoDispersal-package.Rd

Documents the workflow and processes involved in the analysis of data for the paper 'The role of conidia in the dispersal of Ascochyta rabiei', https://doi.org/10.1007/s10658-020-02126-2.
